Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:28.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}Sappy old remedies 確信なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:32.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}それでも go up the river
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:35.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}しがみつく became a ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:38.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}涙にさえ灯る日が
